text: Arthur Delaney is a track runner formerly with the Oregon Duckshttp://www.oregonlive.com/trackandfield/index.ssf/2016/01/wednesday_morning_news_notes_l_28.html He ran in the Olympic Trials in 2016.http://www.oregonlive.com/trackandfield/index.ssf/2016/07/teen_sprinting_phenoms_noah_ly.html who competed at multiple NCAA championships.http://www.statesmanjournal.com/story/sports/2016/06/29/olympic- trials-breakdown-local-male-track-and-field-athletes/86501770/ He was a gold medalist at the 2012 World Junior Championships in Athletics – Men's 4 × 100 metres relay ==References== Category:Living people Category:Place of birth missing (living people) Category:Year of birth missing (living people) Category:Oregon Ducks men's track and field athletes
